es/1012/101228-A-XXXXP-001-h.jpg |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2010-12-27 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110616050234/http://www.pacom.mil/web/PACOM_Resources/img/slideshow_images/1012/101228-A-XXXXP-001-h.jpg |archivedate=June 16, 2011 |df=mdy }}</ref>\n|-\n|[[File:Tong-il Security Medel Ribbon.svg|60px]]\n|[[Order of National Security Merit]] ([[South-Korea]]) [[Tong-il Medal]]\n|-\n|[[File:GER Bundeswehr Honour Cross Gold ribbon.svg|60px]]\n|[[Badge of Honour of the Bundeswehr|Bundeswehr Gold Cross of Honor]]\n|-\n|[[File:Noribbon.svg|60px]]\n|''(Unidentified)''\n|-\n|[[File:GA National Guard Commendation Medal.png|60px]]\n|[[Georgia (U.S. state)|Georgia]] Commendation Medal \u2013 ''State of Georgia, USA; Presented to BG Casey by LTC Frank Williams, 3ID ROC, Georgia Army National Guard \u2013 while in Slavonski Brod, Croatia, 1996''\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Expert Infantry Badge.svg|110px]]\n|[[Expert Infantryman Badge]]\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Master Parachutist badge (United States).svg|80px]]\n|[[Parachutist Badge (United States)|Master Parachutist Badge]]\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Ranger Tab.svg|70px]]\n|[[Ranger Tab]]\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Joint Chiefs of Staff seal.svg|75px]]\n|[[Office of the Joint Chiefs of Staff Identification Badge]]\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:United States Army Staff Identification Badge.png|65px]]\n|[[Army Staff Identification Badge]]\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Multi-National Force-Iraq ShoulderSIeeveInsignia.jpg|65px]]\n|[[MNF-I]] [[Combat Service Identification Badge]]\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:10th INF DUI.png|50px]]\n|[[10th Infantry Regiment (United States)|10th Infantry Regiment]] [[Distinctive Unit Insignia]]\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:ArmyOSB.jpg|55px]]\n|5 [[Overseas Service Bar]]s\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Fallschirmspringerabzeichen der Bundeswehr in Bronze.jpg|110px]]\n|[[German Parachutist Badge]] in bronze\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Brevet Parachutiste.jpg|